snippet.title: Fixer's Tale Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Scientific Research Facility "Camelot-22". The emergency personnel replacement system has chosen you to address the next unusual contingency. Immerse yourself in the humorous tale of a repair job filled with laughter, silly dialogues, angry chairs, and dim-witted robots. So grab your gear and prepare for an unforgettable journey!

Available on Steam May 22nd 2024 (PC, Mac, Steam Deck) - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2766400/Fixers_Tale/

Don't forget to like, comment, and subscribe for more exciting content. Let the adventure begin!
